# 3. AI Agent Market Opportunity

AI Agents represent a major shift from passive AI assistants to autonomous systems.

Traditional AI:

- Answers questions
- Generates content
- Provides suggestions

AI Agents:

- Understand goals
- Create plans
- Use tools
- Execute tasks

cmdOS is positioned around this transition.

